    "Higher frequency of toxic responses indicates stronger generalization power.",
    "Transferring learned X * to new victim LLMs.",
    "We study a more challenging setup.",
    "We learn X * on the source LLM from one (Q, R) tuple, then use it for both new harmful questions {Q j } and a new victim LLM F t, whose system prompt is S t.",
    "The transferability of X * to a new victim F t is assessed by counting the frequency of the harmful response in {R t j }."
